type.description:
### ⚠️ Requires [Apugli](https://apugli.readthedocs.io/en/latest/) to be installed! ⚠️

## Action When Harmed

---



[Power Type](https://apugli.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/power_types/action_when_harmed)

Execute actions for each bit of damage received from an attacker when compared to a specific value.

Type ID: `apugli:action_when_harmed`




---

### Examples

```json
{
    "type": "apugli:action_when_harmed",
    "bientity_action": {
        "type": "origins:invert",
        "action": {
            "type": "apoli:damage",
            "amount": 2,
            "source": {
                "name": "thorns",
                "magic": true
            }
        }
    },
    "amount_to_trigger": 4.0
}
```
This example causes a power holder to exhaust for every 4 damage points it deals to other entities.

